{"tid":1976141,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"傻眼！劉樂妍涉賄選被起訴 開庭卻向檢察官宣揚共產黨","createTime":"2020-04-17T04:50:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T05:18:29.000Z","uid":202340,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"747fc61363f7632667ee9d79f539e3f4c0319059","tid":1976141,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T04:50:01.000Z","msg":"2020-04-17 11:58:34<br />\n〔記者陳慰慈／台北報導〕有「女版黃安」之稱的藝人劉樂妍於2018年間，因涉嫌要房客去投票給當時參選台北市議員的羅智強，就減收對方1千元租金，今被台北地檢署依違法選罷法起訴，離譜的是，向來親中的她，每次開庭時也不忘向檢察官宣揚共產黨的好，行徑令人傻眼。<br />\n<br />\n北檢接獲網友舉報後，2018年立案偵查，因劉樂妍長期在中國發展，常不在台灣，因此開庭均約定於她返台期間，而檢察官就此案前後共開過三次庭。<br />\n<br />\n今年2月，武漢肺炎疫情開始延燒，看到中國的防疫措施後，劉樂妍在臉書發文表示「共產黨治國真的是讓我長見識了」，大聲對中國示愛：「天呐，我真的好喜歡中國共產黨哦！你叫我怎麼能不愛你呢？我以前不認識你，自從認識你以後，我瘋狂愛上你！我想我會一輩子愛你！」<br />\n<br />\n據了解，檢察官每次傳喚劉開庭時，她常偏離訊問主題，極力宣傳共產黨治國有方，沒疫情又安全，並強調「我沒有那麼支持國民黨，只是想打敗民進黨，我最支持的其實是共產黨」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/3136786\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F3136786&d=5Vq0xNKZ3qFPdYugipJU93qjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=af023e98\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F3136786&h=aeb4dd5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/3136786</a>"},{"pid":"b25328ce83a3bc138efe80dddde94581e8b4b8eb","tid":1976141,"uid":34457,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T04:55:37.000Z","msg":"咁就抵坐啦"},{"pid":"a166fe53614b9b63df1e7b2af50fa9c22c3a7ff4","tid":1976141,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T04:58:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3551/3551652.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3551%2F3551652.jpg&h=4e8e2eba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7666ea07c4bdbb357ac61e0b97cd716c694449a8","tid":1976141,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a166fe53614b9b63df1e7b2af50fa9c22c3a7ff4","tid":1976141,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T04:58:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3551/3551652.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3551%2F3551652.jpg&h=4e8e2eba&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T05:18:29.000Z","msg":"屌你咩 搞到我嘔返噚晚餐飯出嚟"}]}